Always question frauds in the name of personal opinion speaking bullshit , when 100 people love a product 20 might not like it , but your strategy of targeting a brand that 100 people are speaking positive about and intentionally speaking negative about it in the name of personal opinion shows how low you can go to gain trust and fame overnight 😂 

we as a brand might not address some positive reviews, but we always address every single negative review when brought to our notice, because we care about each and every costumer , from start that’s us , but since Jan we have been getting attacked with such plants and fakes all the time🙏🏼

It’s funny how they thought we won’t find out, if you’re doing fake stuff and getting people to order from us , at-least use accounts with faces and educate them about the product na 🤣 . 

You might be thinking it’s just 20 k loss of money to order products and plant negative reviews to bring a good brands reputation down by doing such cheap stunts , but what you don’t know is we are using your own 20 k to grow and build 🤣✌🏻 

So all the best , you can’t stop us . Our customers will come chasing you all down , because we are not just a brand , we are community of hustling men who focus on truth and growth .
